What profession have you done?
I worked in IT Company, where I was administrator, programmer, user support and teacher. Currently I work in Savremena Komerc (Payment Control Services) as dispatcher, but IT was my job passion for so long. If you are interested, I can send you my Information folder, where is about my IT COmp. work, so you can see it. My work focused on projector installations in different part of republic of Serbia.
I also work as administrator in local company, Stage 9 rhythm group, organising events and musical festivals. I was first assistant in organization and administration of seventh days of musical scene Dubrovnik 1999, founded Cirque De Soleil show Devils road 2005, Backyard Folk 2006, and second assistant in organization Republic of Batak 2007. I helped in organization movie festival called Settlers in village Drumkeen 2015.
How do you spend your free time?
Due to my working timetables, I don't have much free time. I'm planning to take an English language course, because I want to practice speaking in English. For now, I'm planning to buy a bike for cycling, and I hope to invest that more
